Author: maxencetajet
Description: BTCUSD -- 5 min

 BUY POSITION

1 : The price is above the ema
2 : A buy signal appears on the HalfTrend (blue triangle)

 SELL POSITION

1 : The price is bellow the ema
2 : A sell signal appears on the HalfTrend (red triangle)
